Name: django-vegetarian-cookbook
Version: 1.0.8
Summary: Django application for the publication of vegetarian culinary recipes with the calculation of energy and nutrients.
Home-page: https://github.com/sergey-panasenko/django-vegetarian-cookbook
Author: Sergey Panasenko
Author-email: sergey.panasenko@gmail.com
License: AGPL v3
Description: ##############################
        Django Vegetarian Cookbook
        ##############################
        
        
        Django application for the publication of vegetarian culinary recipes with the calculation of energy and nutrients.
        
        ********
        Features
        ********
        
        * manage ingridients, include ingridient nutrients and energy
        * manage additional meashures
        * manage recipes
        * recipe category
        * recipe tag
        * show recipe
        * calculate recipe energy
        * search recipes by many parameters
        
        
        ************
        Installation
        ************
        
        pip install django-vegetarian-cookbook
        
        add apps in settings.py
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            INSTALLED_APPS = [
                ...
                'vegetarian_cookbook',
                'bootstrap4',
                'ajaximage',
                'imagekit',
                'ckeditor',
            ]
        
        add url in urls.py
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            from django.conf.urls import include
        
            urlpatterns = [
                path('', include('vegetarian_cookbook.urls')),
                path('admin/', admin.site.urls),
            ]
        
        more info see in example app
        
        https://github.com/sergey-panasenko/django-vegetarian-cookbook
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
